class.comment: Represents a type of access for a Registry.

enumerations.name: STATIC
enumerations.comment: The registry is currently frozen and read-only.

enumerations.name: WORLDGEN
enumerations.comment: The registry is used for world generation.

enumerations.name: DIMENSIONS
enumerations.comment: The registry is used for a world type.

createRegistryAccess.comment: Creates a layered registry access from all of these values.
